Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:07.81,Default - Top,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 2414, Omi Beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:05.74,sign_1511_2_N_1_Grand_Prix,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,N-1 Grand Prix
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.63,Default,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,Final group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:12.23,Default,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.80,Default,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,2425, Bonnou Illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:17.96,Default,FUKUMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:18.97,Default,KONDO,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.68,Default,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. If your name was called...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.39,Default,BABA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got something after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.49,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.71,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Nagashima, right? You came to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:41.18,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you do the joke \Nabout the café hideaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.87,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a musician, I wouldn't put \Nmy hit songs on my "best of" albums.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.62,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you haven't succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.18,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:50.25,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,you have to be someone that has \N"best of" albums with hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.76,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get enough time \Nto go over our material, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:55.73,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you guys might make it \Nsince Baba-san's getting popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.33,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, Bonnou Illumination\N took that category.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:01:59.86,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you up in my personal space,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.51,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,but you're also trying to burn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.31,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a smoking area in Shin-Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:08.16,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The population density of smoking \Nareas in Shin-Osaka is brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.62,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta watch out for all \Nthe lit cigarettes everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.41,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me explain the joke. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.69,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You should team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.73,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.00,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You're splitting up this year \Nif you don't make it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.02,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I promise we'll make it big together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.31,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I can even write jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.51,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You used a ton of my letters \Non your radio show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:23.43,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw out your best qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.95,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I can show you the view \Nfrom the top, Shibagaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.02,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If I team up with a high school student now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.58,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,people will say I've finally lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.44,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going do \Nafter you split up, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.42,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can make it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.37,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.55,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,How obnoxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.03,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,As loud and annoying \Nas a convenience store ATM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.80,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that shrill piercing sound \Nthey make after you withdraw money...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.79,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not that funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.60,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't draw\N out my best qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.76,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're splitting up, team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.61,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's still the losers' bracket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.56,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You're not giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.67,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.28,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you wanna be an entertainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.44,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,find someone your own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.11,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to ride my flimsy-ass coattails.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.36,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw you perform your jokes today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.33,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like Baba-san has lost his \Nmotivation for manzai comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.01,Default,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,So you should try again with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:14.13,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Got interesting news from our\N unlicensed doc, y'know the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.15,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Dobu-san showed up\N in a fancy new ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.51,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Shot in the femoral region, \Nright in the thigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.98,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the culprit's \Nthe one who stole his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.59,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,If the boss finds out, Dobu better run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.59,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, his points are\N goin' down one-by-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.74,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,After this, all his business will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.56,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,We used to be brothers in arms,\N fates entwined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.39,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Two flowers blossoming \Nfor the boss, both aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.40,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,He taught me to use people\N and money, rinse and repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.11,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Showed compassion to a country \Nkid raised on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.09,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,But I gotta say, this development\N is pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.77,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,A decade my senior, he had\N my respect, my affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.93,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's gone soft, \Na sugar-coated confection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.54,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,What is Dobu-san worth now? Upon inspection...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.74,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,He lacks punch, like these candy \Ndrops, to make a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.51,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for peppermint, \Nbut all I find is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.33,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready for a big explosion \Nto knock me off my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.42,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored. Light me on fire, \Nput me in the hot seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.17,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Sekiguchi, your lack of experience\N led to defeat. You were sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.00,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,So, deliver this declaration of war for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.25,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a scramble for that\None billion yen spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:03.31,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the loser will get\Nto watch his criminal career drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.64,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll pass on the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:13.19,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, did you take a look \Nat that Nikaido fan account?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:21.69,sign_6071_81_Imai_Nikaido_fan,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Imai@Nikaido fan account
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.95,Italics,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,"The photo of the jackpot-winning ticket \NI posted before was actually edited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:21.69,Italics,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I lied to get a response from Rui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.28,Italics,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.52,Italics,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue running this \Nas a Rui Nikaido fan account.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.33,Italics,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble I caused."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.76,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, no problem. The one billion \Nyen is definitely with Imai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.42,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen these digital black \Nand white shadows online.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.69,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very famous amateur mistake, \Ndoes he think he's sly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.24,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Look into his past, dig up what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.74,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,And figure out where we can find the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:46.00,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll get everyone on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:51.13,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for calling you so often, Odokawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:56.06,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,The guy offering to pay 900 million \Nfor your dash cam data is a yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.64,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Accepting money from him would \Nmean problems for you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.51,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let us handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.51,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to compensate \Nyou appropriately,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.70,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,and we can guarantee \Nyour safety, Odokawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.79,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you this for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.21,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going great for \NMystery Kiss right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.87,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I came prepared today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.85,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to use force if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting to show your true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.42,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. I obviously wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.05,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I came to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.31,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mystery Kiss that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.43,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are. Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.85,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about money \Nanymore. It's our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.93,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.81,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad. I was rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.38,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What's too bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.57,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That Ichimura had to run badger games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.53,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.08,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Kakihana is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:51.02,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, he's a hopeless \Nidiot. It was his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.74,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But he paid for his mistake already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.87,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, then? \NHave you gotten what you deserve yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.04,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Odokawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.73,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.22,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Explain what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.72,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Our side of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:14.17,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, we'll apologize \Nto Kakihana-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.73,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, could you turn left here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.33,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa-san, how do you want to handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:23.48,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in exposing you \Nto the public or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.75,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that. Next right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:34.10,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone about your evil doings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.29,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is all over, I'll even \Ngive you my dash cam data.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.21,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,In other words?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.94,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you side with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.98,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Betray whoever you're working for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.08,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Park the car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.43,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, betray?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:04.02,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're after the one billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.35,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.75,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I'm going to take down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:13.99,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,both whoever's behind you \Nand the guy behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.56,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.53,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I've considered the situation \Nas calmly as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.78,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What we have to gain, what we have to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.70,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,The power balance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.28,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I look at it, \NI don't see how...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:35.26,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,a single taxi driver can beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.93,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.56,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you and take everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.33,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.46,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.31,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.49,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you'll get a martelo to the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.53,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Capoeira's actually pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.89,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You thought it was \Na type of dance, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.16,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you even start doing \Nit in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.37,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my top three things that I don't \Nunderstand how people get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.53,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What are the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.93,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hammer throw and stimulants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:49.04,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You need to apologize to everyone \Nand everything, starting with Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.50,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.41,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:57.45,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Both for this, and everything until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.00,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've seen saying from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.30,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I even told you my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.54,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,To betray Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.64,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.54,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,And if I do, Mystery Kiss will be protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.73,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If things go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.28,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she doesn't want \Nto run badger games.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.61,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.97,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Allow yourselves to be caught by the police \Nwhile you're stealing the one billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.05,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:26.26,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Won't I be arrested then, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:29.40,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe. Tell them you were threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.35,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, aren't you {\i1}actually{\i0} \Nbeing threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:34.76,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of a problem for me if they \Nask why I was being threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.96,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,They've got dirt on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.31,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:41.22,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't help me, I'm turning \Nyou in to the police now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:45.23,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,For robbing a taxi, running badger games, \Nabduction, and confinement...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.64,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.31,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only way to protect Mystery Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.04,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:01.58,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll contact you \Nonce our plans are made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.46,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Goriki told me what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.34,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.62,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already involved. \NI don't have a choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.44,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working with Dobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.63,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:25.52,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Lately I've been thinking that Dobu \Nmight not be such a bad guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:30.19,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He operates based \Non his brand of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:34.61,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But then I thought this must be \Nsome kind of brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.21,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't been freed from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.23,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he's done \Na lot of bad things,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.81,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,but his dedication to his boss never wavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.28,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu-san's been brainwashed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.37,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I decided. I just decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.66,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to punish him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.88,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.54,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for defending Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.47,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't defending him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:57.66,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But in the real world, good isn't always \Nrewarded, and evil isn't always punished—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.86,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I told you to stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.59,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't get involved, you'd \Nbe dead by now, Odokawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.81,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,And why'd you call me Odokawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.72,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to call you "Odokawa-san" \Nbecause there's too much I want to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.85,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're texting. \NHow is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.85,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, what do you mean, \Nit's none of my business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.13,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I saved your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.40,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to break my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.67,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second time in a short period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.30,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:27.01,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,For unrelated reasons, a guy armed \Nwith a gun is trying to kill me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:30.54,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,When did your life suddenly \Nbecome so hard-boiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:37.05,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he's able to determine my \Nlocation to an unnatural degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.53,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he planted a GPS on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.72,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:45.18,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,After my car window was broken, \Nsomeone fired a shot into my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.89,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unnaturally plain way \Nto harass someone, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.26,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit probably suddenly \Nfound me around the city
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:54.86,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,and hid a phone in my car \Nas a temporary measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.40,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But a phone would run \Nout of battery eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.95,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,So they found my home, broke \Nmy car window, retrieved their phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.27,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,and then replaced it \Nwith a battery-less GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.20,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:12.54,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,They're still trying to kill you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.60,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find a way \Nto use this against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.51,sign_2158_2_Equator_Sauna,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Equator Sauna
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.51,sign_17755_229_Eiji_Kakihana,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Eiji Kakihana
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.51,sign_17755_230_Heading_to_the_s,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Heading to the sauna. Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.51,sign_17755_231_Wish_I_could__bu,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Wish I could, but I'm working tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.51,sign_17755_232_Good_for_you__wo,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, working two jobs. \NWe can go once you've paid off your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.51,sign_17755_233_That_ll_be_years,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be years from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.11,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,Was it cold outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.84,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.37,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is already December.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:47.93,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,Sudden changes in body temperature \Ncan be really dangerous. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.01,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,It's called heat shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.69,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.58,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.18,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,This place is always empty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.64,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.54,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Tough guy with his tattoos out \Nfor everyone to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.88,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,That was eye-opening. \NImpressive as always, Odokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.26,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.39,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,Because people thought you \Nwere the kidnapper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.22,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,in the missing Nerima high school girl case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.84,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a cop? No, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.12,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I suspected you, taxi driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.01,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.82,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,I still think there's a 5% chance \Nyou did it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:29.70,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa, do you not want money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.81,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully, I don't have money problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.48,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I do have one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.87,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want more than befits my stature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:39.75,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is to be able to repay the people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:43.34,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,who helped me, little by little, \Nto the best of my own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.09,Default,KURODA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.94,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, we've found Imai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:12.58,sign_20232_260_Imai_Nikaido_fan,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Imai@Nikaido fan account
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:12.58,sign_20232_261_I_ve_got_nothing,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing to do, so I've been \Nwatching Mystery Kiss' concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:08.48,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,He tweeted this on November \N15th after moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.43,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,If you raise the volume, \Nyou can faintly hear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.58,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,the departure melody \Nof a train in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.71,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,In Tokyo, the stations that use this melody
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:18.95,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,are Komagome Station and Musashi-Koganei \NStation on the Yamanote Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.76,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,He also responded to a tweet from \Nsomeone who seems to be his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:29.76,sign_20643_268_Taro_Matsu___mat,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Taro Matsu \N{\c&H969696&}@matsutaro_123     2 days ago \N{\b0\c}Seriously? This Christmas Mystery Kiss \Nconcert is first come, first served?\N\N {\b1}Imai@Nikaido fan account \N{\c&H969696&}Replying to @matsutaro_123\N {\b0\c}It takes 50 minutes to get there \Nfrom my place so I'm leaving at noon lol{\c}{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:26.11,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Kiss is performing a concert \Nat the civic center on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:30.14,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Since it takes him 50 minutes to get there, \Nhe must be at Musashi-Koganei Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.05,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Returning to the tweet \Nhe made the day he moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.49,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,we looked for rental properties \Nwith similar wallpaper
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:39.35,sign_20933_272_Finished_moving_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Finished moving. Unpacking is gonna suck. \NBut I put up my Rui-tan poster first thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:39.35,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,within hearing distance of the \NMusashi-Koganei Station departure melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.15,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,This "Rinky-Dink Koganei" apartment \Nbuilding fits the criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:50.99,sign_21175_276_Rinky_Dink_Kogan,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Rinky-Dink Koganei #201
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:46.55,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the scenery visible from his window \Nand the positions of the utility poles,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:50.58,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,he's at Rinky-Dink Koganei, room 201.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:56.79,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,While I expanded my vocabulary, \Nyou cyberstalked him excellently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.37,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd get it done, but I gotta admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.85,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,it gives me chills, creeps me out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.77,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding, well done. \NSeriously, great stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.84,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go grab this guy by the scruff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.18,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Bad blood's brewing, but it's too \Nsoon to cause an uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:15.01,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu-san underestimates me \N'cause he thinks I'm an herbivore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.00,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll peel back his disguise \Nand stab him with all my spines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:21.41,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Seize the big money and \Nlaugh out loud like a porcupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:29.44,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure Yano and his guys found Imai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.89,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yamamoto the manager contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:35.92,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They'll act as soon as tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:40.24,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take Imai to the bank \Nand keep him locked up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.37,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,until the bank gets one \Nbillion in cash ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.74,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,The bank's supposed to \Ncontact you if Imai arrives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:49.74,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They'll tell me the time and date \Nthat the cash will be handed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:53.04,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You ready? I'm about \Nto tell you my entire plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.10,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you drum it \Ninto your head, Odokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:55.93,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.69,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,The one billion yen will be split \Ninto ten duraluminum cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.24,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,but the bank will hand \Nover just one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:06.44,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They'll also hand over nine duraluminum \Ncases filled with fake bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:17.24,sign_23104_301_Real,SIGN TOP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Real
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:17.24,sign_23104_302_Fake,SIGN BOTTOM,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Fake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.93,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's crew will probably be \Nwith Imai during the handoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.53,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,and they'll want to confirm that it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.27,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're giving them \None case of real bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:19.37,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Yano will want to get out of there as soon \Nas possible, so he won't check all ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.43,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Once Yano's crew pack 100 million real yen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.06,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,and 900 million counterfeit yen \Ninto their car and leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:28.46,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as they leave, \NI'll acquire 900 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.16,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, you've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.01,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't end there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.54,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They've issued a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.03,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to steal the 100 million they took.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.10,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.71,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,The bank is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:45.18,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Wait in your taxi at this nearby parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.00,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.16,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to the parking lot \Nwith 900 million yen in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:52.78,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You'll move your taxi, \Nand I'll park in your spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.07,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll get into your taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.74,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Where do we head next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.95,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably head to\N their hideout at the wharf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:04.65,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Along the way, Big Daimon's patrol car \Nwill probably stop them around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.85,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're using every service vehicle you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:11.87,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,When Big Daimon searches their car, \Nhe'll find a ton of counterfeit bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:16.69,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,After dropping me off nearby, \Nyou'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.12,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,While Yano and the police are making a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.68,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrive on the scene \Nand steal Yano's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.06,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,After confirming I have the 100 million, \NI'll get back into your taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.44,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head back to the parking lot where \Nthe car with 900 million is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.58,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we screw up, you'll just be \Na taxi driver transporting his passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.36,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.99,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,And that's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.63,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I call it... ODDTAXI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're acting like \Nthat's supposed to sound cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.34,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,ODDTAXI...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.43,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.45,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,"Odd" refers to one of a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.84,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Without you or me, this plan doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.65,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,After acquiring the one billion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:59.96,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,and paying the two bank employees \Nwho helped us 100 million each,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.20,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,we'll split the rest. Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:05.89,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any. I already \Ngave you all my conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.55,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't want any?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.69,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Your risk of being arrested isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.86,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Just do something about Skull Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.07,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Then my relationship with you will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:19.66,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Mask's target might be me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.63,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,He actually shot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:26.33,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That would be ideal. \NI want to return to my normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:29.57,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Once this operation is over, \Nwe'll go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.88,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's nearly over, \Ntell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.63,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.85,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What's this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:39.04,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,A screenshot from your dash cam data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:42.00,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the missing Nerima high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.95,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Your boss' classmate's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:48.98,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,No, but she's the only one from your dash \Ncam data that matches her description.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:51.05,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.11,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You drove her two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:58.87,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I've driven her before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.58,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Mystery Kiss girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.10,Italics,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Yano will go after Imai tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.26,Italics,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,After that, they'll go to the bank \Nto begin the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.46,Italics,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,and then confine him at their wharf hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:22.58,Italics,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, Sekiguchi, and I will \Nbring Imai to the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.51,sign_27860_368_Fuyuki_Yamamoto,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Fuyuki Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:25.51,Italics,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,at a time and date determined \Nby them and leave with the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.98,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Dobu predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.97,Italics,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.85,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.32,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.33,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,When they hand over the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:38.11,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,they'll probably check the contents \Nof just one of the duraluminum cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:43.22,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as they're finished, \NI want you to tell the bank employees,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:46.41,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,"Let us check another one."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.39,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Will they be giving us counterfeit bills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.73,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It should make Yano's crew freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.57,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Play along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.71,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,The police will handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.31,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the police that they threatened you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.17,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:04.61,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you can call the police, \Nthey'll arrest Yano for blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:08.97,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're participating in a crime, \NI doubt you'll get off scot-free,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:12.05,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,but at the very least, you'll have \Nprotected Mystery Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.76,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can protect \NMystery Kiss, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.57,sign_29229_387_Little_Daimon,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Little Daimon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.50,sign_29517_388_Rinky_Dink_Kogan,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Rinky-Dink Koganei
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:37.20,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:41.80,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, Odokawa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:46.10,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be brief. The yakuza \Nare coming here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.26,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:52.02,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it is, but you can't \Nrun. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.35,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.74,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,They'll threaten you \Nand take you to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.68,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do as they tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:00.50,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,For about one week after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:04.37,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be imprisoned at their hideout \Nuntil the cash is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:10.55,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,But the Mystery Kiss CD release date \Nand concert are in just over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.31,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Try to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.91,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,After imprisoning you, they'll take you \Nto the bank to receive the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:18.15,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'll be hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.54,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,but until then, I need you to do \Nwhat Yano's crew tell you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:24.93,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If you can make it that far, \Nthey'll be arrested by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:29.17,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If you can be patient for one week, \Nboth you and Mystery Kiss will be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.17,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.45,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Odokawa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:36.69,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best for Mystery Kiss, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.86,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I only got \Nthis money because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.91,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I had before all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:46.21,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose it, my life will \Njust go back to how it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.20,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep on supporting Mystery Kiss, \Njust like I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.87,sign_31390_414_17th_Principal__,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,17th Principal - Tadashi Oda \N\N16th Principal - Kazuta Fujimoto\N\N 15th Principal - Hideo Takemoto \N\N14th Principal - Joji Taga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.86,Default,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,You're Odokawa-kun's doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:58.25,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's a lack of \Ninformation about his accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.86,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking around about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.21,Default,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Is he seriously ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.75,Default,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,His accident was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:15.59,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,The body found in the Tokyo Bay \Nin October has been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:21.94,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is Nerima City resident \NYuki Mitsuya-san, 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:25.23,sign_32175_422_Nerima_City__Tok,SIGN TOP RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Nerima City, Tokyo\N {\fs18}Yuki Mitsuya-san (18)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:25.23,sign_32175_423_Breaking_News,SIGN FAR LEFT BOTTOM,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking News
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:25.23,sign_32175_424_Shibaura_Wharf_A,SIGN BOTTOM,0000,0000,0000,,Shibaura Wharf Abandoned Body Case\N {\fs20}Body Identified as Belonging \Nto Member of Popular Idol Group
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:28.15,Default - Top,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuki Mitsuya-san was a member \Nof idol group Mystery Kiss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:32.15,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,Fans have been shocked by \Nthe sudden news of her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:33.58,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not her...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:50.66,Next_Time,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: {\fs22\b1}If We Could Go Back to That Day{\fs\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.46,Italics,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Since I was a child, I've hated \Nlosing more than others."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:39.54,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, don't read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:40.60,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In fact, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.85,Italics,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm thinking about entering \Na training school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.74,Italics,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll turn the comedy industry on its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:47.77,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"I didn't ask for this kind of Santa Claus." \NWhat kind of Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:48.66,Italics,NAGASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Give me two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:49.94,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Forget it!